(9143, 421, 'campus_description', 'VHIO is one of the three scientific research institutes that belong to the <a href=\"https://www.vallhebron.com/en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Vall d\'Hebron Barcelona Hospital Campus</a> together with the Vall d\'Hebron Hospital and the Autonomous University of Barcelona (UAB). The interplay between these institutions aims at providing the best patient care through excellence research and innovation practices applied to clinical healthcare. You can check the campus map <a href=\"https://www.vallhebron.com/en/map\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">here</a>.'),
