(13149, 561, 'sections_0_blocks_0_block_2_content', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-156\" src=\"https://vhiovidaprogramme.eu/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/the-project-research.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"366\" />\r\n\r\nThe programme will consolidate the research career opportunities of the beneficiaries while strengthening the training portfolio of VHIO Academy and expanding VHIO’s network of partner organisations to foster interdisciplinary and intersectoral cancer &amp; Oncology research.'),
